heaviest_rainrate.status: 11.8mm per hour was the peak rain rate recorded today ranking 5th in our overall records.  The storm lasted 2.1 hours and 7.28mm of rain fell. summary.description:

The past week and month had observable variation in rainfall (down 0.1 mm), cloud levels (up 1266 m), and light levels (up 6593 lux) when compared to today.
